Class HandlersDispatcherServlet

java.lang.Object
  javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
          com.alexkasko.rest.handlers.HandlersDispatcherServlet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig
public class HandlersDispatcherServlet
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet

Dispatcher servlet for handlers, delegates GET, POST and PUT dispatching to HandlersDispatcher. Accesses dispatcher through ServletContext using mandatory init parameter dispatcherKeyInServletContext. Uses UTF-8 as default encoding for request and response.

Author:
alexkasko Date: 3/18/12
See Also:
HandlersDispatcher, Serialized Form
